---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Venue & Travel | Cloud Identity Summit 2026">
    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-16 px-4 overflow-hidden flex-grow text-center">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-2xl h-[400px] bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-900/30 via-blue-900/5 to-transparent blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="inline-block bg-blue-900/30 border border-blue-800/50 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-6">
                <span class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">Location</span>
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight leading-tight mb-8">
                Venue & Travel
            </h1>
            
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Join us right in the heart of Europe. The venue is located in Frankfurt-Niederrad, offering excellent connectivity and making it incredibly easy to reach from anywhere in the world.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 pb-32 w-full relative z-10">
        
        <div class="bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-blue-500/30 rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-12 mb-16 shadow-2xl shadow-blue-900/10 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center relative z-10">
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 aspect-square bg-slate-800/80 rounded-2xl border border-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center text-6xl shadow-inner">
                    🏢
                </div>
                <div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">The Venue: adesso SE</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        The Cloud Identity Summit 2026 will take place at the modern adesso SE offices, located in the striking <a href="https://www.prisma-frankfurt.de/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline transition-colors">Prisma building</a>. Expect excellent facilities, great catering, and plenty of room for networking.
                    </p>
                    <div class="bg-slate-950/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-4 inline-block">
                        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-1">Location</p>
                        <p class="text-white font-semibold">adesso SE, Prisma Frankfurt-Niederrad</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            
            <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-slate-900/60 transition-colors">
                <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🚄</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">By Train</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm mb-4">
                    The venue is just a few minutes' walk from the <strong class="text-slate-200">Frankfurt-Niederrad</strong> station. Niederrad is excellently connected and can be reached in about 10 minutes from Frankfurt Central Station (Hauptbahnhof) via S-Bahn or regional trains.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-slate-900/60 transition-colors">
                <div class="text-4xl mb-4">✈️</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">By Plane</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    Frankfurt Airport (FRA) is Germany's largest airport. From there, you can reach the Frankfurt-Niederrad station in just about 10 minutes via the suburban train (S-Bahn), making your international arrival incredibly smooth.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-slate-900/60 transition-colors">
                <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🚗</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Car & Parking</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    If you prefer to travel by car, Frankfurt is perfectly connected to the German Autobahn network. Details regarding specific on-site parking options in the Niederrad office district will be provided closer to the event.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-slate-900/60 transition-colors">
                <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🏨</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Accommodation</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    We highly recommend the <strong class="text-slate-200">Crowne Plaza Frankfurt - Congress Hotel</strong>, which is conveniently located just a 10-minute walk from the venue. We will publish details regarding potential room contingents here soon.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>